     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "YoungContent[{i1, i2, ..., in}] returns the content of n-tuple {i1, i2, \
..., in} of ik \\[Element] [d], where d is the maximum number in the tuple. \
YoungContent[{i1, i2, ..., in}, k] gives the multiplicity of the first k \
letters. YoungContent[wt] returns the content (or type or weight) of Weyl \
tableau wt, i.e., a list of multiplicities of letters appearing in the Weyl \
tableau. YoungContent[wt, k] gives the multiplicity of the first k letters.", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "YoungContent", 
